CA: Your mind is teeming with ideas,

00:03:09.845 --> 00:03:11.196
and not just randomly.

00:03:11.220 --> 00:03:13.426
They're carefully linked together.

00:03:13.450 --> 00:03:16.355
Collectively they form
an amazingly complex structure

00:03:16.379 --> 00:03:18.553
that is your personal worldview.

00:03:18.577 --> 00:03:20.863
It's your brain's operating system.

00:03:20.887 --> 00:03:22.759
It's how you navigate the world.

